description: This file implements functions related to the platform-dependent and utility aspects of the Psm Sys Registry within the Persistent Storage Manager (PSM) component of the CCSP platform. It mainly provides a factory function to create a Sys Registry object, with references to external global headers.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE PsmCreateSysRegistry(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new Sys Registry object using the parameters provided. It acts as a wrapper around the PsmSysroCreate function.
